de.lmu.ifi.dbs.elki.evaluation.scores

Class PrecisionAtKEvaluation

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.lmu.ifi.dbs.elki.evaluation.scores.AbstractScoreEvaluation
      • de.lmu.ifi.dbs.elki.evaluation.scores.PrecisionAtKEvaluation
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ScoreEvaluation

    public class PrecisionAtKEvaluation
extends AbstractScoreEvaluation
    Evaluate using Precision@k, or R-precision (when k=0). When k=0, then it is set to the number of positive objects, and the returned value is the R-precision, or the precision-recall break-even-point (BEP).
    Since:
    0.7.0
    Author:
    Erich Schubert
